  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to Senate",
    "asOf": "2022-12-05",
    "date": "2022-12-21T13:45:09Z",
    "text": "Quadrennial Homeland Security Review Technical Corrections Act of 2021\n\nThis bill makes numerous changes to the quadrennial homeland security reviews. The quadrennial homeland security review is the Department of Homeland Security's capstone strategy document, which offers recommendations on long-term strategy and priorities for homeland security.\n\nSpecifically, the changes are related to consultation, prioritization, resources required, deadlines, and documentation."
